(2837, 'widget_w-introduction-3_html_desc', 'A 510 cartridge typically consists of a mouthpiece, tank or chamber, and a built-in battery. The mouthpiece is where you draw the vapor, while the tank houses the cannabis extract and the heating element, which vaporizes the extract. The built-in battery powers the vape pen, ensuring a consistent flow of power without any blocks or interruptions.\r\n\r\nThe atomizer, a small heating element, plays a crucial role in the vaping process. It vaporizes the cannabis extract, providing an efficient and consistent vaping experience without any Ingress Protection (IP) concerns.\r\n\r\nNow that we understand the components of a 510 cartridge, let’s explore how to ensure compatibility with your vape battery.', 'off'),
(2838, '_widget_w-introduction-3_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
(2839, 'widget_w-introduction-3_img', '467', 'off'),
(2840, '_widget_w-introduction-3_img', 'field_66bb7b7314434', 'off'),
(2841, 'widget_w-introduction-3_css_class', 'home-info-section sccomponents section-padding', 'off'),
