(2865, 'widget_w-introduction-4_html_desc', 'The key to compatibility between 510 cartridges and vape batteries lies in the standard 510 thread. Any cartridge featuring a standard 510 thread can be used with any standard 510 threaded battery. In fact, it is estimated that 99% of batteries and cartridges, including those containing various cannabis extracts, are interchangeable.\r\n\r\nTo ensure compatibility between your 510 cartridge and vape battery, simply make sure that both the battery and cartridge have a standard 510 thread. This will allow you to choose the right combination for your vaping needs and enjoy a seamless experience.', 'off'),
(2866, '_widget_w-introduction-4_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
