(2883, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(2890, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_html_desc', 'Our 510 cartridges offer a high concentration of THC, allowing users to find the perfect balance for their preferences and needs. The THC concentrations in these cartridges range from 90-95%, while the CBD concentrations range from 0-2%. This versatility caters to both recreational and medicinal users.', 'off'),
(2891, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_html_desc', 'field_66bc076e2ccdd', 'off'),
(2892, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_icon', '473', 'off'),
(2893, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_icon', 'field_66bb8443ab0d8', 'off'),
(2894, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_title', 'High THC Cartridges', 'off'),
(2895, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_title', 'field_66bb8459ab0d9', 'off'),
(2896, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_content', 'High THC cartridges contain a higher proportion of THC compared to CBD, offering a more powerful and enduring experience than other cannabis products. These cartridges are composed of pure, potent flower extract and boast a high THC concentration, resulting in a thick consistency and a distinct aroma.\r\n\r\nWhile high THC cartridges provide a more potent experience, they also come with potential disadvantages. They may be more costly than other cannabis products and potentially more difficult to locate. Problem solved with TEN$CARTS.', 'off'),
(2897, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_0_fc_content', 'field_66bb848cab0da', 'off'),
(2898, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_icon', '472', 'off'),
(2899, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_icon', 'field_66bb8443ab0d8', 'off'),
(2900, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_title', 'Precise Dosing', 'off'),
(2901, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_title', 'field_66bb8459ab0d9', 'off'),
(2902, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_content', 'A vape pen allows you to control your dosage with precision. By adjusting the frequency, intensity, and duration of your puffs, you can modulate your intake—short, light draws for a milder experience, deeper inhales for a potent hit.\r\n\r\nAdvanced batteries even let you twist the heat settings to fine-tune your usage. Lower temperatures give subtler effects, while higher ones offer a stronger impact.\r\n\r\nThis potency control, coupled with the mantra of “start low, go slow,” assures a personalized, safer cannabis experience. With each puff, you’re not only enjoying the product but also crafting your ideal balance.', 'off'),
(2903, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_list_content_1_fc_content', 'field_66bb848cab0da', 'off'),
(2904, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_bgimage', '210', 'off'),
(2905, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_bgimage', 'field_66bc074f2ccdc', 'off'),
(2908, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_heading', 'THC Concentrations in TEN$<span>CARTS</span>> 510 Cartridges', 'off'),
(2909, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-3_fc_heading', 'field_66bc084a40054', 'off'),
(2939, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_heading', 'How to Use a 510 Cartridge', 'off'),
(2940, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_heading', 'field_66bc084a40054', 'off'),
(2941, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_html_desc', 'Using a 510 cartridge is a straightforward process. Start by removing any packaging and attaching the cartridge to a compatible vape battery. Once securely attached, adjusting settings and employing proper inhalation techniques will ensure a smooth and enjoyable vaping experience.\r\n<br>\r\nLet’s explore these steps in more detail in the following subsections.', 'off'),
(2942, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_html_desc', 'field_66bc076e2ccdd', 'off'),
(2943, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content', '3', 'off'),
(2944, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content', 'field_66bb83f66299e', 'off'),
