(2947, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_css_class', 'linkbox_list-section scstep-product section-padding', 'off'),
(2948, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(2951, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_icon', '475', 'off'),
(2952, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_icon', 'field_66bb8443ab0d8', 'off'),
(2953, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_title', 'Step One<br> Attaching the Cartridge', 'off'),
(2954, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_title', 'field_66bb8459ab0d9', 'off'),
(2955, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_content', 'To attach your 510 cartridge to a compatible vape battery, first remove any packaging from the cartridge. Then, simply align the cartridge and the battery, turning the cartridge clockwise to secure it to the battery. Make sure the cartridge is firmly attached and installed correctly to prevent any issues during use.\r\n\r\nPay attention to the connection between the cartridge and the battery to ensure a secure fit. Check that the cartridge is firmly attached and installed correctly to avoid any issues during use.', 'off'),
(2956, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_0_fc_content', 'field_66bb848cab0da', 'off'),
(2957, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_icon', '474', 'off'),
(2958, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_icon', 'field_66bb8443ab0d8', 'off'),
(2959, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_title', 'Step Two<br> Adjusting Settings', 'off'),
(2960, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_title', 'field_66bb8459ab0d9', 'off'),
(2961, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_content', 'Once your cartridge is securely attached, you can adjust the settings on your vape device to optimize performance with your 510 cartridge. To do this, press the button on the battery three times to change the voltage. The voltage can be set between 2.0 and 4.0V, we recommend starting low.\r\n\r\nAdjusting the voltage is important because it allows you to tailor the vaping experience to your liking. Different voltage settings can yield various flavors and effects, so experimenting with these settings can help you find the perfect balance for your preferences.', 'off'),
(2962, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_1_fc_content', 'field_66bb848cab0da', 'off'),
(2963, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_icon', '476', 'off'),
(2964, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_icon', 'field_66bb8443ab0d8', 'off'),
(2965, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_title', 'Step Three<br> Proper Inhalation Techniques', 'off'),
(2966, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_title', 'field_66bb8459ab0d9', 'off'),
(2967, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_content', 'When it comes to inhalation, timing is crucial. To ensure optimal inhalation of your 510 cartridge, press and hold down the button on your battery while inhaling gently through the mouthpiece on the cartridge. Allow a half-second pause before commencing the inhale and release the button a second or two before completing the hit.\r\n\r\nExhaling slowly and steadily is also important to clear the vapor from your lungs and avoid feeling overwhelmed. Proper inhalation and exhalation techniques help ensure that you get the full effect of the vapor without overdoing it, leading to a more enjoyable and satisfying vaping experience.', 'off'),
(2968, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-4_fc_list_content_2_fc_content', 'field_66bb848cab0da', 'off'),
(2980, 'widget_text-4_css_class', 'sctext-safety container-fluid section-padding', 'off'),
(2981, '_widget_text-4_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(2988, 'widget_w-introduction-5_html_desc', 'One of the main distinctions between vaping and smoking is that smoking involves the combustion of tobacco to deliver nicotine, whereas vaping does not involve burning. This results in vaping aerosol containing only a small fraction of the 7000+ chemicals found in tobacco smoke.\r\n\r\nBased on the available evidence, smoking appears to be more detrimental to one’s health than vaping.', 'off'),
(2989, '_widget_w-introduction-5_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
(2990, 'widget_w-introduction-5_img', '477', 'off'),
(2991, '_widget_w-introduction-5_img', 'field_66bb7b7314434', 'off'),
(2992, 'widget_w-introduction-5_css_class', 'home-info-section scinfo-white reverse section-padding', 'off'),
(2993, '_widget_w-introduction-5_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(2995, 'widget_w-introduction-6_html_desc', 'Practicing responsible use is essential when utilizing 510 cartridges to prevent potential accidents and misuse that could cause harm to you or those around you. This includes using the cartridge until it finishes off to avoid leaks that could damage the battery or vape pen. Refilling the cartridge may also result in leaks and should be avoided.\r\n\r\nAlways prioritize safety and responsible use when enjoying your 510 cartridge vaping experience.', 'off'),
(2996, '_widget_w-introduction-6_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
(2997, 'widget_w-introduction-6_img', '478', 'off'),
(2998, '_widget_w-introduction-6_img', 'field_66bb7b7314434', 'off'),
(2999, 'widget_w-introduction-6_css_class', 'home-info-section scinfo-white section-padding', 'off'),
(3000, '_widget_w-introduction-6_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(3018, 'widget_text-5_css_class', 'sctext-understanding sctext-popular container-fluid section-padding', 'off'),
(3019, '_widget_text-5_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(3034, 'widget_w-introduction-7_html_desc', 'Sativa dominant cartridges, offer energizing and uplifting effects. These cartridges are ideal for users seeking a cerebral, stimulating experience, often employed during the daytime for their invigorating effects. Sativa dominant cartridges may also provide relief from stress and anxiety, as well as physical pain.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re seeking a boost in productivity or a creative spark, sativa dominant cartridges can offer an energizing experience that may prove advantageous for various activities. Keep in mind, however, that the effects of these cartridges may vary between individuals, so it’s essential to start with a low dose and gradually adjust as needed.', 'off'),
(3035, '_widget_w-introduction-7_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
(3036, 'widget_w-introduction-7_img', '479', 'off'),
(3037, '_widget_w-introduction-7_img', 'field_66bb7b7314434', 'off'),
(3038, 'widget_w-introduction-7_css_class', 'home-info-section sccomponents-two sccomponents reverse section-padding', 'off'),
(3039, '_widget_w-introduction-7_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(3042, 'widget_w-introduction-8_html_desc', 'Flavored cartridges offer a unique vaping experience, providing a variety of flavors such as fruit, candy, and menthol for users who prefer to enjoy the taste of their vape without the harshness of the smoke. These cartridges contain e-liquids with added flavorings, typically food-grade, and can range from candy/dessert, fruit, or fruit-ice combination flavors.\r\n\r\nWhile flavored cartridges can provide a more enjoyable taste experience, it’s important to keep safety and health considerations in mind when using these products. Be mindful of the potential health risks associated with vaping and always store cartridges appropriately to prevent nicotine poisoning.', 'off'),
(3043, '_widget_w-introduction-8_html_desc', 'field_66bb7b3d14433', 'off'),
(3044, 'widget_w-introduction-8_img', '480', 'off'),
(3045, '_widget_w-introduction-8_img', 'field_66bb7b7314434', 'off'),
(3046, 'widget_w-introduction-8_css_class', 'home-info-section sccomponents-two sccomponents section-padding', 'off'),
(3047, '_widget_w-introduction-8_css_class', 'field_64f1a97cb531b', 'off'),
(3056, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-5_fc_heading', 'Troubleshooting Common Issues', 'off'),
(3057, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-5_fc_heading', 'field_66bc084a40054', 'off'),
(3058, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-5_html_desc', 'As with any device, you may encounter some common issues when using 510 cartridges, such as leakage, clogging, or battery contact problems. Don’t worry!\r\n\r\nIn the following subsections, we will provide troubleshooting tips to help you address these issues and ensure a smooth vaping experience.', 'off'),
(3059, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-5_html_desc', 'field_66bc076e2ccdd', 'off'),
(3060, 'widget_w-linkboxlist-5_fc_list_content', '2', 'off'),
(3061, '_widget_w-linkboxlist-5_fc_list_content', 'field_66bb83f66299e', 'off'),
